little bro."}, {"start": 576.96, "end": 578.96, "text": " So what?"}, {"start": 578.96, "end": 580.96, "text": " I said how tough are you if the cameras aren't rolling?"}, {"start": 580.96, "end": 582.96, "text": " As tough as you want me to be."}, {"start": 583.0400000000001, "end": 585.0400000000001, "text": " Well, we throw down."}, {"start": 585.0400000000001, "end": 587.0400000000001, "text": " Are you like that mad you lost a football game?"}, {"start": 587.0400000000001, "end": 589.0400000000001, "text": " No, the game's still going."}, {"start": 589.0400000000001, "end": 591.0400000000001, "text": " It's not still going."}, {"start": 591.0400000000001, "end": 593.0400000000001, "text": " I mean, if you want to be honest, what position do you play?"}, {"start": 593.0400000000001, "end": 595.0400000000001, "text": " In what?"}, {"start": 595.0400000000001, "end": 597.0400000000001, "text": " In football."}, {"start": 597.0400000000001, "end": 599.0400000000001, "text": " I haven't played football in like eight years."}, {"start": 599.0400000000001, "end": 601.0400000000001, "text": " Then why do you care so much about the game?"}, {"start": 601.0400000000001, "end": 603.0400000000001, "text": " Hey, don't touch the camera. I advise not to."}, {"start": 603.0400000000001, "end": 605.0400000000001, "text": " You started touching Matt."}, {"start": 605.0400000000001, "end": 607.0400000000001, "text": " I don't give a s**t."}, {"start": 607.0400000000001, "end": 609.0400000000001, "text": " Oh, he's famous? Well, I don't remember asking."}, {"start": 609.12, "end": 611.12, "text": " I really don't care."}, {"start": 611.12, "end": 613.12, "text": " I'm not a cloud demon."}]}